<headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 07 at 4:01PM CDT  by NWS QuadCities</headline>
<description>...Hot and Humid Conditions Late This Afternoon and Evening...
Air temperatures in the mid 80s to near 90 combined with
dewpoints in the mid to upper 70s, will produce heat indices in
the upper 90s to around 100 for the rest of this afternoon and
early evening. Make sure to drink plenty of water and take
frequent breaks if outdoors. Remember to check the backseat
before you lock car doors.</description>
